== MusixmatchApiParser.py ==

Rhythmbox lyrics plugin, to install it you need to:

- edit LyricsSites.py in the Rhythmbox lyrics plugin directory adding
  from MusixmatchApiParser import MusixmatchApiParser

  and in lyrics_sites list the dictionary
  { 'id': 'musixmatch.com',	'class': MusixmatchApiParser,	'name': _("musiXmatch (musixmatch.com)")	}

- copy the script file in the same directory and run the program.


== musixmatch.lua ==

VLC lyrics plugin, to install it you need to:

- copy the script in the directory ~/.local/share/vlc/lua/extensions/
